---
By: Sivananda
Locus:
  Page: 294
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - To live is the rarest thing in the
---
Life is a journey from impurity to purity, from hatred to cosmic love, from
death to immortality, from slavery to freedom, from imperfection to
perfection, from pain to eternal bliss, from diversity to unity, from
ignorance to eternal wisdom, and from weakness to strength.
